{"tid":1967243,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"神秘男寶雅苑墮樓身亡","createTime":"2020-04-10T18:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:40:47.000Z","uid":69678,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"04008c191d7e198d09ffffa224a187afda8e36be","tid":1967243,"uid":69678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:49:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200411/bkn-20200411001845865-0411_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3xGaZmRcijKXjiOTh_Pnh43Nf2bEjl11FyFCCoZSgNSOmm4VXydJwtmFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200411%2Fbkn-20200411001845865-0411_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3xGaZmRcijKXjiOTh_Pnh43Nf2bEjl11FyFCCoZSgNSOmm4VXydJwtmFA&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=2834a5c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200411/bkn-20200411001845865-0411_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3xGaZmRcijKXjiOTh_Pnh43Nf2bEjl11FyFCCoZSgNSOmm4VXydJwtmFA</a><br />\n<br />\n今日(11日)凌晨零時許，警方接獲報案，指有一名男子在大埔寶雅苑興和閣高處墮下，昏迷倒臥大廈對開地上。消防接報趕至，替事主進行心外壓急救，惟經救護員檢查後，最後證實他傷重不治，隨即用白布遮蓋遺體。警方封鎖現場，經初步調查，相信事件無可疑，正調查事主身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=9da5664a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n又冇可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係白粉報即時報導"},{"pid":"0cd04f6900f888f72c72940fb9938dcf99b65463","tid":1967243,"uid":45772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:51:40.000Z","msg":"尋晚十點幾有衝鋒車經過嗰頭，唔知關唔關事"},{"pid":"3f4b5949329abff1b20c8f4bf6e45d543668d91a","tid":1967243,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike